title: Document AI - Try Document AI
abstract:
# Document AI - Try Document AI
# Try Document AI
Use the following demo to return annotations for your document file.
- Maximum file size is 20 MB.
- [File types](/document-ai/docs/file-types) accepted: PDF, GIF, TIFF, JPEG, PNG, BMP, WEBP.
- [Maximum pages](/document-ai/quotas#processor_limits) vary per processor.
- [Supported languages](/document-ai/docs/languages) vary per processor.
- Your browser must have JavaScript enabled.
#
content:
